                    <msContents>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1ra" to="5vb"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7032Trinity">Fragment of an Amharic treatise on the Trinity</title>
                            <note>The beginning is missing. An indeterminate number of leaves is lacking between <locus target="#1"/> and
                                <locus target="#2"/>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="am">
                                <supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">አ</supplied>ብ፡ እንደ፡ ልብ፡ ነው፡ ወልድ፡ እንደ፡ ቃል፡ ነው፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እንደ፡ እስትንፋስ፡ ነው። 
                                ልብ፡ ቃል፡ ወእስትንፋስ፡ እንዳይለሐሐቁ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አይለዋወጡም። 
                                ልብ፡ ቃል፡ ወእስትንፋስ፡ እንዳይለያዩ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አይለያዩም። 
                                እምቅድመ፡ <pb n="1rb"/> ዓለም፡ እንዴኽ፡ ነበሩ፡ ዓለም፡ ከኀለፈም፡ እንዴኽ፡ ይኖላናሉ፡ ይኽም፡ ይኽት፡ ፀሐይ፡ ም፡ ሐንድ፡ ነው፡ በሐንደነቱ፡ ግን፡ 
                                ሶስትንት፡ አለበት፡ አብ፡ ክበቡን፡ ይመስል፡ ወልድ፡ ብርሃኑ፡ ይመስል፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሙቀቱ፡ ይመስል። አብነም፡ ስለመሰሉት፡ በክበቡ፡ እንደ፡ 
                                ፀሐ<pb n="1va"/>ይ፡ ውሱን፡ ክበብ፡ አይዶለውም፡ የሰማዩም፡ ሰማይ፡ የዕመቁ፡ ም፡ ዕመቅ፡ የጽንፉ፡ ም፡ ጽንፍ፡ አይወሰነውም፡ ወልድነም፡ በብርሃኑ፡ 
                                ስለመሰሉት፡ ውሱን፡ ብርሃን፡ አይዶለውም፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus target="#2r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3013RepCh293">Hymn to the Church</title>
                            <note>The beginning is missing. The poem is apparently inserted in the middle of <ref target="#ms_i1"/>.</note>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez">ለኪ፡ ዘአፈይኩ፡ ስብሐተ።
                                አምሳለ፡ ቍርባን፡ ተወካፊ፡ ሊተ።
                                ወተረፈ፡ ቃልየ፡ ወትረ፡ ረስዪ፡ መሥዋዕተ።
                                ስብሐት፡ ለኪ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በኆልቈ፡ እስትንፋስ፡ ወነገር።
                                ስብሐት፡ ለኪ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በኆልቈ፡ አዕፅምት፡ ወጸጕር።
                                ስብሐት፡ ለኪ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በኆልቈ፡ ሐዋሳት፡ ዓሥር።
                                ስብሐት፡ ለኪ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ዘአብሐኪ፡ እግዚአብሔር።
                                በላዕለ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወደሙ፡ ክቡር።</explicit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <locus from="6ra" to="12vb"/>
                            <title>Turkish and Arabic vocabulary</title>
                            <note>As a whole indicated by: <foreign xml:id="ti"><title>ነገረ፡ ትርኵ። ዓ።</title></foreign> written on the upper
                                margin. Both texts are published in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/HE8H4U2Z"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Littmann1908AbessGlossen"/><title level="a">Abessinische Glossen (Zum Teil nach Kopien von C. Bezold)</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Assyriologie und Vorderasiatische Archäologie</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Enno</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Littmann</t:surname></author><date>1908</date><biblScope unit="volume">21</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">1–2</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">50–109</biblScope><note type="url">https://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/titleinfo/118035</note></bibl>.</note>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1">
                            <locus target="#6ra"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/NAR0184ForeignWords">Tigrinya-Turkish Vocabulary</title>
                            <note>Containing only eight words.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="ti">ነዓ፡ ብሂል፡ ዢል፤
                                ተቀመጥ፡ ብ፡ ውቱር፤
                                ሀባ፡ ብ፡ ዠትር፤
                                አልቦን፡ ብ፡ ያክትር፤
                                ሀሎ፡ ብ፡ ዮል፤
                                ኪድ፡ ብ፡ ቢናዓደም፤
                                መጽአ፡ ብ፡ ገልድ፤
                               </incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="ti"> ኬደ፡ ብ፡ ደልዳል።</explicit>
                            <textLang xml:lang="ti"/>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2">
                                <locus from="6ra" to="12vb"/>
                                <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/NAR0184ForeignWords">Tigrinya-Arabic Vocabulary</title>
                                <note>Containing several words on <locus target="#6ra"/> with a special ancient form of the letter 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="ti">ዥ</foreign> with small strokes in every of the four edges: 
                                    <figure><graphic url="https://betamasaheft.eu/resources/images/snippets/BLorient12996/sign1.png" height="30px">
                                            </graphic></figure></note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="ti">ነዓ፡ ብሂል፡ ተአል፤
                                    ተቀመጥ፡ ብ፡ አይዥልስ፤
                                    ተንሥእ፡ ብ፡ ጉም፡ ቁምሂ፤
                                    ኪድ፡ ብ፡ ሩሕ፤
                                    ኬድኩ፡ ብ፡ ሮሕ፡ 
                                    ኬደ፡ ብ፡ ራሕ፡ መሻ፤
                                    ተመልሰ፡ ብ፡ ገለበ፤
                                </incipit>
                                <textLang xml:lang="ti"/>
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem> 
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="13ra" to="15va"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7031HymnJesus">Hymn to Jesus Christ</title>
                            <note>The beginning is missing.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አምጻኤ፡ ዓለማት፡ በኪኑ።
                                ወልድ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በምኵናኑ።
                                መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘኢይትሌለይ፡ ሥልጣኑ።
                                ለሥላሴሆሙ፡ ዘኢይትረከብ፡ ወሰኑ።
                                ወህላ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ዌ</supplied>ሆሙ፡ ተከሥተ፡ ለመኑ።
                                ስብሐት፡ ለከ፡ ወልደ፡ አብ፡ ቅዳሚ።
                                በፅኑዕ፡ ኀይልከ፡ መሠረተ፡ ዓለም፡ ሐታሚ።
                                እትሜከህ፡ ልሐኵተከ፡ እንዘ፡ ኪያከ፡ እሰሚ።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="15va" to="16va"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7030SalamYoungFathers">Salām</title>
                            <note>Partly illegible; spaces intended to be written in red were left blank.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ሰላም፡</supplied> ለከ፡ ለውርዝዋን፡ አበው፡ 
                                <gap reason="omitted"/> ወልዶሙ። እለ፡ ወለዱከ፡ በልሕቅናሆሙ። መርዓት፡ ስነ፡ ገድሎሙ።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
